trans-unit.source: Represents the resolution supported by a printer.
trans-unit.target: 프린터에서 지 원하는 해상도를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: This class is used by the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties to get the printer resolutions that are available on the printer and to set the printing resolution for a page, respectively.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스에서 사용 되는 <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName>및 <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName>가져올 프린터에서 사용할 수 있는 프린터 해상도 페이지에 대 한 인쇄 해상도 각각 설정 하는 속성.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> property to determine whether the printer resolution type is the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> value <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>속성 <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>값 <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> 프린터 해결 유형 인지 확인을</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> 사용 하 여

trans-unit.source: If so, use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A> properties to determine the printer resolution in the horizontal and vertical directions, respectively.
trans-unit.target: 그렇다면 사용 하는 <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A>및 <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A>속성을 가로 및 세로 방향으로 프린터 해상도 각각 확인 합니다.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A>

trans-unit.source: `dmPrintQuality` is a member of the `DEVMODE` (device mode) structure, which defines constants that map to printer quality settings.
trans-unit.target: `dmPrintQuality`멤버인는 `DEVMODE` (장치 모드) 구조를 프린터 품질 설정에 매핑되는 상수를 정의 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The X property contains the value `DMRES_HIGH` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_MEDIUM` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_LOW` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, and `DMRES_DRAFT` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.
trans-unit.target: X 속성 값이 들어 `DMRES_HIGH` 경우 <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>로 설정 되어 <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_MEDIUM` 경우 <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>로 설정 되어 <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_LOW` 경우 <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>로 설정 되어 <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, 및 `DMRES_DRAFT` 경우 <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>를 <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>
